### 7. Get Product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### 8. Get User Cart (Requires Auth Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. Add Item to Cart (Requires Auth Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 10. Update Cart Item (Requires Auth Token)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/cart/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 3
}

### 11. Remove Item from Cart (Requires Auth Token)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/cart/remove/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 12. Get User Profile (Requires Auth Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
